channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Kamala Chameleon: Will the Real Kamala Harris Please Stand Up?
Wes Moore praises Walz for military service, completing 'mission' despite retirement outrage
item.description: Maryland Gov. Wes Moore celebrated Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz's military career as evidence he will complete the election "mission," despite outrage from vets over Walz's military retirement.

item.title: Giuliani to Newsmax: Tim Walz's China Ties, Socialist Views Problematic
item.description: Former New York Mayor Rudy Giuliani took aim at Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz during an appearance on Newsmax's "Greg Kelly Reports," raising questions about Walz's ties to China and his political ideology. Giuliani didn't mince words when discussing the governor's past visits to...

item.title: New Details About What Hunter Biden Spent Money on Instead of Taxes Revealed at Pre-Trial Hearing
Kamala Harris to accept presidential nomination on final night of DNC
item.description: Vice President Harris will accept the Democrat presidential nomination on Thursday night at the DNC in a historic moment after President Biden dropped out of the race.

item.title: Gov. Burgum to Newsmax: DNC a 'Hollywood-style Lovefest'
item.description: The Democrat National Convention in Chicago is a beguiling event set up to distract from the issues surrounding Vice President Kamala Harris, North Dakota Republican Gov. Doug Burgum told Newsmax on Wednesday.

item.title: Tim Walz's DNC Speech: 20 Minutes of Utter Lies, Stolen Valor
'Star Wars' actor Mark Hamill weighs in on Kamala Harris' chances of victory
item.description: Actor Mark Hamill briefly spoke with Fox News Digital about the Harris-Walz ticket on his way into a VIP event at the Democratic National Convention.

item.title: San Francisco GOP Chair to Newsmax: City Used to Elect Centrists
item.description: The chair of San Francisco's Republican Party told Newsmax Wednesday how progressives ended up running the city.

GOP veteran-lawmakers drop scathing 'stolen valor' letter to Walz as Trump camp rips 'Freakish Timothy'
item.description: The Trump campaign gave journalists a letter it published on X and sent to Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz blasting him over claims of stolen valor.

item.title: Jim McLaughlin to Newsmax: Left-Leaning Polls 'Expose Themselves'
item.description: Some of the polls being hawked by left-leaning news outlets "a lot of times expose themselves because ... they're not transparent," pollster Jim McLaughlin said.

item.title: Still a Rock Star in His Party, Bill Clinton Praises the Next Generation
Gus Walz brought to tears, shares emotional moment with father Tim during DNC speech: 'That's my Dad'
item.description: VP candidate Tim Walz's son Gus was brought to tears Wednesday at the Democratic convention where he shared an emotional moment with his father during the keynote speech.

item.title: UAW President Fain Snubs Unbridled Immigration's Impact on Unions
item.description: United Auto Workers (UAW) President Shawn Fain recently downplayed concerns about the effects of mass immigration on labor unions, brushing aside worries about the record number of migrants encountered at U.S. borders during the Biden-Harris administration.
